                451.3393295857139,
                766.5888203024095,
                14.162765035839357
            ],
            "text": "During the current financial year, the Group recognized an impairment loss of Rmb 10,371 (US$1,695) (2012: Rmb Nil) ",
            "font": {
                "color": [
                    0,
                    0,
                    0,
                    255
                ],
                "name": "/QSMABI+MyriadPro-Regular",
                "size": 1
